Loading Data

data = load("Latent_data.RData") 


a = table %>%
  dplyr::select(starts_with("H")) 

set.seed(123)
sample1 = sample(a, 30) 

sample1[] <- sapply(sample1, as.numeric) 

sample1 = sample1 %>%
  na.omit()

set.seed(333)
sample2 = sample(a, 30)

sample2 = sample2 %>%
  na.omit()
